                         Privacy Policy
1. This application has the function of connecting to the Internet, but it is only used for data transmission in game.
2. If personal information is collected, it will be used for program updates, event announcements or instant notifications.    
3. If personal information is used, it is used to help program development, delivery and improvement of products, services, content and advertising.  
4. We guarantee that we will not disclose user personal information to any third party without statutory procedures or the user's prior permission.
